wdi-DT.NFL.IMFN.CD.def: Net financial flows received by the borrower during the year are disbursements of loans and credits less repayments of principal. IMF is the International Monetary Fund, which provides nonconcessional lending through the credit it provides to its members, mainly to meet balance of payments needs. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-DT.NFL.IMFN.CD.name: Net financial flows
